02:02:38.970 --> 02:02:40.500
at all stations at all times.

02:02:42.370 --> 02:02:46.270
With regard to maintenance, NATO recommends full monthly checks.

02:02:48.070 --> 02:02:49.030
And weekly street checks.

02:02:50.170 --> 02:02:52.970
