02:02:53.030 --> 02:02:55.700
be wise. And this could be on the order of

02:02:55.700 --> 02:02:56.930
every one to three days.

02:02:58.400 --> 02:03:00.600
The ordinance should also specify what.

02:03:01.400 --> 02:03:03.030
