02:03:07.470 --> 02:03:09.300
doing what they said they were going to do.

02:03:13.400 --> 02:03:16.370
So we also recommend that the city of south Portland

02:03:16.400 --> 02:03:17.370
reserve the right.

02:03:18.370 --> 02:03:21.970
To approve key aspects of the system design in some

02:03:21.970 --> 02:03:22.000
cities.

02:03:22.970 --> 02:03:24.600
