02:03:38.970 --> 02:03:42.270
Or annual membership that could reduce the cost for frequent

02:03:42.270 --> 02:03:42.670
riders.

02:03:43.700 --> 02:03:46.570
And cash payment options to reduce access barriers.

02:03:47.870 --> 02:03:51.670
Barriers, notably. We really want to ensure that the pricing

02:03:51.800 --> 02:03:53.230
is affordable for short trips.

02:03:54.170 --> 02:03:56.270
